---
By: Meister Eckhart
Locus:
  Page: 358
  Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Perfection
---
People look in vain places for peace. They seek it in the world outside, in
places, people, ways, activities. ...but there is no peace found this way.
They are looking in the wrong direction, and the longer they look the less
they find what they are looking for.
